::Shadow Wing::

She slowly opened her eyes.  Lunarpine had her wing pinned to the 
ground.  She turned her head to see the tree had fallen next to her.  
She turned back to look at Lunarpine. She was slightly dazed by the 
fall but assest the situation quickly.  With her wing pinned, he won 
this round. She sighed, "You win this round beloved." She raised her 
head and lightly touched her beak to his nose.
"Now if you would please let me up."
